<funcs>
  <func>
    <title>GetAction</title>
    <category>Objects</category>
    <subcat>Activity</subcat>
    <version>4.6.5.0 CP</version>
    <syntax><rtype>string</rtype></syntax>
    <desc>Returns the name of the current activity of an object. If the object is currently not active, the return value is "Idle".</desc>
    <examples>
      <example><code><funclink>if</funclink>(<funclink>FindObject</funclink>(Find_ID(Clonk))-&gt;GetAction() == &quot;Swim&quot;) <funclink>Log</funclink>(&quot;Toll, irgendein Clonk schwimmt&quot;);</code></example>
    </examples>
